{"title":"Linux命令","slug":"Linux命令","date":"2023-10-25T03:18:00.000Z","updated":"2023-10-25T14:36:13.588Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux命令.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":" [Figure] ","covers":["/images/linux.png","/images/postsImg/3.png","/images/postsImg/4.png"],"content":"<p><img src=\"/images/linux.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p><strong>快捷键</strong><br><strong>ctrl+ins\t\t\t复制\t\t星标</strong><br><strong>shift+ins\t\t\t粘贴\t\t星标rmrm</strong><br><strong>命令</strong><br><strong>uname \t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看系统内核</strong><br>**lsb_release -a\t\t\t**\t\t<strong>查看系统版本</strong><br><strong>cat &#x2F;etc&#x2F;issue\t\t\t\t\t\tLinux系统和版本</strong><br><strong>sudo passwd\t\t\t\t\t\t重置密码</strong><br><strong>su\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t输入密码root</strong><br><strong>useradd 用户名\t\t\t\t\t新建用户\tsudo passwd 新建用户密码</strong><br><strong>su 用户名\t\t\t\t\t\t切换用户</strong><br><strong>shutdown -r now\t\t\t\t\t重启</strong><br><strong>halt\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t关机</strong><br><strong>ls\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看目录</strong><br><strong>cd\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t进入文件夹</strong><br><strong>cd ..\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t返回上一级</strong><br><strong>mkdir\t\t\t\t\t\t\t建立文件夹\t（mkdir 文件夹名）</strong><br><strong>rmdir\t\t\t\t\t\t\t删除文件目录（不包括文件）</strong><br><strong>rm -rf\t\t\t\t\t\t\t删除文件夹包括文件</strong><br><strong>rmdir –help\t\t\t\t\t\t删除文件命令提示帮助</strong><br><strong>rm\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t删除文件</strong><br><strong>nano 文件名\t\t\t\t\t\t创建文档\tnano里 ctrl x\t文件保存</strong><br><strong>cat 文件名\t\t\t\t\t\t查看</strong><br><strong>mv 文件名 &#x2F;目录\t\t\t\t\t移动</strong><br><strong>mv 文件名 新名字\t\t\t\t\t重命名</strong><br><strong>cp 文件名 路径\t\t\t\t\t复制文件</strong><br><strong>cp -r\t\t\t\t\t\t\t复制文件夹包括文件</strong><br>** -p\t\t\t**<br><strong>ctrl c\t\t\t\t\t\t\t撤销</strong><br><strong>clear\t\t\t\t\t\t\t清屏</strong><br><strong>ifconfig\t\t\t\t\t\t\t获取IP地址</strong><br><strong>ls -a\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t显示所有文件 带点的是隐藏文件</strong><br><strong>ls -l\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看权限 大小 时间</strong><br><strong>ls ~\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t用户当前位置</strong><br><strong>find &#x2F; -name “<em>文件名</em>“\t\t\t\t查找文件</strong><br>**whereis 名字\t\t\t\t\t\t查找\t\t\t\t**<br><strong>lsof -i\t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看所有端口</strong><br><strong>curl\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t访问网站</strong><br><strong>curl -k icanhazip.com\t\t\t\t查看外网ip（访问网站的方式）</strong><br><strong>unzip\t\t\t\t\t\t\t解压zip</strong><br><strong>tail -f 文件名\t\t\t\t\t\t查看实时日志（-n 行数）</strong><br><strong>free -m\t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看内存</strong><br><strong>top -p 端口\t\t\t\t\t\t查看指定pid使用内存</strong><br><strong>top free\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCPU和内存使用情况</strong><br><strong>lsof -i\t\t\t\t\t\t\t端口占用</strong><br><strong>netstat -tunlp |grep 端口\t\t\t用于查看指定的端口号的进程情况</strong><br><strong>netstat -anp |grep 端口</strong><br><strong>netstat -ntlp</strong><br><strong>netstat -tln</strong><br><strong>其他命令</strong><br><strong>nohup npm start &amp;\t\t\t\t后台运行npm</strong><br><strong>后台执行</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ctrl+z</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 后台运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">bg</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 查看后台进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">jobs</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 断开linux连接</span><br><span class=\"line\">logout</span><br><span class=\"line\">#调回前台</span><br><span class=\"line\">fg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>Java命令</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ps -ef|grep java\t\t\t\t\t\t\t查看java进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">ps -auxw|grep java\t\t\t\t\t\t查看java进程（显示短的参数行）</span><br><span class=\"line\">kill -9 PID \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t强制关闭进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">kill PID\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t关闭进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">java -jar jar包名\t\t\t\t\t\t\t启动jar</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">nohup java -jar XXX.jar &gt;temp.log &amp; </span><br><span class=\"line\">nohup java -jar XXX.jar &gt;log.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;\t\t后台启动jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>查看线上实时日志</strong><br>命令:tail -f catalina.out<br><img src=\"/images/postsImg/3.png\" alt=\"图片\"></p>\n<p><strong>Python命令</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python3 文件.py\t\t\t\t\t#运行\t\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">nohup python -u 文件.py &gt; 文件.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;\t\t#后台运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">nohup python3 -u 文件.py &gt; myLog.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;\t\t#后台运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">nohup python3 -u server.py &gt; myLog.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;\t\t#后台运行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>权限</strong><br><strong>x1执行 w2写 r4读\t\t\t\tdrwx xr x **<br><strong>chmod 数字 文件名\t\t\t\t修改权限</strong><br><strong>chmod 数字 文件名 -R\t\t\t\t修改权限和所有子目录</strong><br>444 r–r–r–<br>600 drw——-<br>644 drw-r–r–<br>666 drw-rw-rw-<br>700 drwx——<br>744 drwxr–r–<br>755 drwxr-xr-x<br>777 drwxrwxrwx<br><strong>编辑文本</strong><br>** vi 文件名</strong><br><strong>编辑完底线命令模式输入英文符号\t：</strong><br><strong>保存\t\t\t\t\t\t\tw</strong><br><strong>退出\t\t\t\t\t\t\tq</strong><br><strong>保存退出\t\t\t\t\t\twq</strong><br><strong>强制退出\t\t\t\t\t\tq！</strong><br><strong>后台运行</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nohup tar czf /data/backup.tgz /data/backup</span><br><span class=\"line\">ctrl+z #挂起到后台</span><br><span class=\"line\">bg #后台执行  可以先通过jobs 查看当前有多少job</span><br><span class=\"line\">ctrl+d  #或者 关闭窗口  进程任然会在后台执行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>Ubuntu</strong><br><strong>Ubuntu安装包工具</strong><br><strong>apt-get update\t更新安装包</strong><br><strong>apt-get install *** \t\t\t\t\t安装</strong><br><strong>apt-get install\topenssh-server\t安装远程服务</strong><br><strong>apt-get remove ***\t\t\t\t\t卸载(后面跟软件名)</strong><br><strong>apt-cache search ***\t\t\t\t在软件包列表中搜索字符串</strong><br><strong>lsb_release -a\t\t\t\t\t查看版本</strong><br><strong>do-release-upgrade -d\t\t\t\t升级ubuntu</strong><br>**Ubuntu ios系统镜像\t\t\t\t**<a href=\"http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu-releases/20.04/\">http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu-releases/20.04/</a>\t（ubuntu-20.04.6-desktop-amd64.iso，desktop桌面）<br><strong>python环境</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt install python3</span><br><span class=\"line\">apt install python3-pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>Ubuntu安装网络工具</strong><br><strong>安装网络工具</strong><br> apt install network-manager\t\t<br><strong>启动</strong><br> systemctl start NetworkManager\t<br><strong>查看网卡信息</strong><br> nmcli connection nmcli con show<br><strong>Ubuntu软件无法从“extensions.gnome.org”下载更新</strong><br><img src=\"/images/postsImg/4.png\" alt=\"图片\"><br><strong>指令</strong><br> sudo add-apt-repository ppa:gnome-shell-extensions&#x2F;ppa sudo apt-get update<br><strong>Ubuntu GNOME 桌面必备扩展（GNOME Shell Extensions）</strong><br> sudo apt-get install gnome-shell-extensions </p>\n","categories":[{"name":"电脑系统","slug":"电脑系统","count":3,"path":"api/categories/电脑系统.json"},{"name":"Linux","slug":"电脑系统/Linux","count":2,"path":"api/categories/电脑系统/Linux.json"},{"name":"Linux命令","slug":"电脑系统/Linux/Linux命令","count":1,"path":"api/categories/电脑系统/Linux/Linux命令.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"命令","slug":"命令","count":3,"path":"api/tags/命令.json"},{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}]}